1. CSS Folder
The CSS folder contains Bootstrap stylesheet files.
It is used for webpage design like colors, buttons, spacing, and layouts.

2. JS Folder
The JS folder contains JavaScript files.
It is used for interactive components like dropdowns, modals, and carousels.

3. Icons Folder
The icons folder contains Bootstrap icons.
It is used to add icons like search, home, and user icons in webpages.
